      "description": "AI-extracted template from reference design",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <title>Design Conversion</title>\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700&family=Montserrat:wght@700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --bg: #F8F7F4;\n            --primary: #000000;\n            --secondary: #A0A0A0;\n            --accent: #00E676;\n            --text: #000000;\n            --text-muted: #A0A0A0;\n            --surface: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            background-color: #e0e0e0; /* Just for visibility if canvas is smaller */\n            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;\n        }\n\n        #canvas {\n            width: 1080px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background-color: var(--bg);\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            color: var(--text);\n        }\n\n        /* Decorative elements */\n        .decorative-shape {\n            position: absolute;\n            opacity: 0.2;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n            pointer-events: none;\n            width: 120px; /* Adjusted size for better visibility */\n            height: 120px;\n        }\n\n        .decorative-shape.top-right {\n            top: 80px;\n            right: 80px;\n            transform: rotate(15deg); /* Slight rotation to match visual */\n        }\n        .decorative-shape.bottom-left {\n            bottom: 80px;\n            left: 80px;\n            transform: rotate(-15deg); /* Slight rotation */\n        }\n\n        .decorative-shape svg {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            stroke: currentColor;\n            stroke-width: 1px;\n            fill: none;\n        }\n\n        .header-text {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 100px;\n            left: 100px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n\n        .headline-area {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 150px;\n            left: 100px;\n            line-height: 1.1;\n        }\n\n        .headline-area h1 {\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 80px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            margin: 0;\n            color: var(--primary);\n        }\n\n        .headline-area h1 span.muted {\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n        }\n\n        .diagram-container {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            width: 500px; /* Diameter of the outer circle of nodes */\n            height: 500px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .center-node {\n            width: 120px;\n            height: 120px;\n            background-color: var(--primary);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 20px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: var(--accent);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2; /* Ensure it's above lines */\n            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--accent); /* Green border */\n        }\n\n        .outer-nodes-container {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            /* Using CSS variables for angles and radius for clarity */\n            --node-radius: 210px; /* Distance from diagram center to outer node center */\n            --node-size: 80px;\n            --half-node-size: 40px;\n            --center-x: 50%;\n            --center-y: 50%;\n        }\n\n        .outer-node {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: var(--node-size);\n            height: var(--node-size);\n            background-color: var(--surface);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            font-weight: 400;\n            color: var(--text);\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            border: 1px solid #E0E0E0; /* Subtle border */\n            z-index: 3; /* Ensure nodes are above lines */\n        }\n\n        .outer-node i {\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n            color: var(--text);\n            width: 24px;\n            height: 24px;\n        }\n\n        /* Positioning for 6 nodes around a circle (clockwise from top) */\n        /* Angles: 0, 60, 120, 180, 240, 300 degrees */\n        .outer-node:nth-child(7) { /* EMAIL (0 deg) */\n            top: calc(var(--center-y) - var(--half-node-size) - var(--node-radius) * cos(0deg));\n            left: calc(var(--center-x) - var(--half-node-size) + var(--node-radius) * sin(0deg));\n        }\n        .outer-node:nth-child(8) { /* CODE (60 deg) */\n            top: calc(var(--center-y) - var(--half-node-size) - var(--node-radius) * cos(60deg));\n            left: calc(var(--center-x) - var(--half-node-size) + var(--node-radius) * sin(60deg));\n        }\n        .outer-node:nth-child(9) { /* FINANCE (120 deg) */\n            top: calc(var(--center-y) - var(--half-node-size) - var(--node-radius) * cos(120deg));\n            left: calc(var(--center-x) - var(--half-node-size) + var(--node-radius) * sin(120deg));\n        }\n        .outer-node:nth-child(10) { /* SCHED (180 deg) */\n            top: calc(var(--center-y) - var(--half-node-size) - var(--node-radius) * cos(180deg));\n            left: calc(var(--center-x) - var(--half-node-size) + var(--node-radius) * sin(180deg));\n        }\n        .outer-node:nth-child(11) { /* DOCS (240 deg) */\n            top: calc(var(--center-y) - var(--half-node-size) - var(--node-radius) * cos(240deg));\n            left: calc(var(--center-x) - var(--half-node-size) + var(--node-radius) * sin(240deg));\n        }\n        .outer-node:nth-child(12) { /* COMMS (300 deg) */\n            top: calc(var(--center-y) - var(--half-node-size) - var(--node-radius) * cos(300deg));\n            left: calc(var(--center-x) - var(--half-node-size) + var(--node-radius) * sin(300deg));\n        }\n\n        /* Dashed lines */\n        .dashed-line {\n            position: absolute;\n            height: 1px;\n            background: repeating-linear-gradient(to right, var(--text-muted) 0, var(--text-muted) 2px, transparent 2px, transparent 6px);\n            transform-origin: left center;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        /* Calculate line positions and rotations */\n        /* Center of diagram: 250, 250\n           Radius of center node: 60px\n           Radius of outer node: 40px\n           Distance from center of diagram to center of outer node: 210px\n           Length of line: 210 - 60 - 40 = 110px\n           The `translateX(60px)` moves the start of the line from the diagram center to the edge of the center node.\n           Angles for rotation are adjusted to point from center node to outer node.\n        */\n        .dashed-line:nth-child(1) { /* To EMAIL (0 deg) */\n            top: 250px;\n            left: 250px;\n            width: 110px;\n            transform: rotate(-90deg) translateX(60px);\n        }\n        .dashed-line:nth-child(2) { /* To CODE (60 deg) */\n            top: 250px;\n            left: 250px;\n            width: 110px;\n            transform: rotate(-30deg) translateX(60px);\n        }\n        .dashed-line:nth-child(3) { /* To FINANCE (120 deg) */\n            top: 250px;\n            left: 250px;\n            width: 110px;\n            transform: rotate(30deg) translateX(60px);\n        }\n        .dashed-line:nth-child(4) { /* To SCHED (180 deg) */\n            top: 250px;\n            left: 250px;\n            width: 110px;\n            transform: rotate(90deg) translateX(60px);\n        }\n        .dashed-line:nth-child(5) { /* To DOCS (240 deg) */\n            top: 250px;\n            left: 250px;\n            width: 110px;\n            transform: rotate(150deg) translateX(60px);\n        }\n        .dashed-line:nth-child(6) { /* To COMMS (300 deg) */\n            top: 250px;\n            left: 250px;\n            width: 110px;\n            transform: rotate(-150deg) translateX(60px);\n        }\n\n\n        .body-text-area {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 250px;\n            left: 100px;\n            width: 400px;\n            font-size: 28px;\n            line-height: 1.4;\n            color: var(--text);\n        }\n\n        .body-text-area .highlight {\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: var(--primary);\n        }\n\n        .footer-left {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 100px;\n            left: 100px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n        }\n\n        .footer-right {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 100px;\n            right: 100px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"canvas\">\n        <!-- Decorative elements -->\n        <div class=\"decorative-shape top-right\">\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\">\n                <path d=\"M 20 80 L 50 50 L 80 80 M 50 50 L 50 20\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 4\" />\n            </svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"decorative-shape bottom-left\">\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\">\n                <path d=\"M 20 80 L 50 50 L 80 80 M 50 50 L 50 20\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 4\" />\n            </svg>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"header-text\">\n            THE VISION\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"headline-area\">\n            <h1>{{headline}} <span class=\"muted\">Zero employees.</span></h1>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"diagram-container\">\n            <div class=\"center-node\">\n                YOU\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"outer-nodes-container\">\n                <!-- Dashed lines (6 total) -->\n                <div class=\"dashed-line\"></div>\n                <div class=\"dashed-line\"></div>\n                <div class=\"dashed-line\"></div>\n                <div class=\"dashed-line\"></div>\n                <div class=\"dashed-line\"></div>\n                <div class=\"dashed-line\"></div>\n\n                <!-- Outer nodes (6 total) -->\n                <div class=\"outer-node\">\n                    <!-- ICON:mail --><i data-lucide=\"mail\"></i>\n                    EMAIL\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"outer-node\">\n                    <!-- ICON:code --><i data-lucide=\"code\"></i>\n                    CODE\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"outer-node\">\n                    <!-- ICON:dollar-sign --><i data-lucide=\"dollar-sign\"></i>\n                    FINANCE\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"outer-node\">\n                    <!-- ICON:calendar --><i data-lucide=\"calendar\"></i>\n                    SCHED\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"outer-node\">\n                    <!-- ICON:file-text --><i data-lucide=\"file-text\"></i>\n                    DOCS\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"outer-node\">\n                    <!-- ICON:message-square --><i data-lucide=\"message-square\"></i>\n                    COMMS\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"body-text-area\">\n            {{body}} <span class=\"highlight\">twelve</span>.\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"footer-left\">\n            Instagram<br>@{{brand_name}}\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"footer-right\">\n            {{cta_text}}\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest\"></script>\n    <script>\n        lucide.createIcons();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
